====Declension====
{{sr-bs-noun|褔芯胁械泻|褭褍写懈|褔芯胁械泻邪|褭褍写懈|褔芯胁械泻褍|褭褍写懈屑邪|褔芯胁械泻邪|褭褍写械|褔芯胁械褔械|褭褍写懈|褔芯胁械泻芯屑|褭褍写懈屑邪|褔芯胁械泻褍|褭褍写懈屑邪}}
*Usage note: ''This masculine word is irregular. '''袎褍写懈''' (people, men) is the plural form of the singular word '''褔芯胁械泻''' (man).  Because of the existence of dual grammatical numbers in Serbian, the dual form (the form for 2, 3, and 4) is '''褔芯胁械泻邪'''.  The dual numbers also apply to any higher numbers ending in 2, 3, and 4, such as 22, 23, and 24.''
*:Example of dual numbers:  ''袛胁邪 褔芯胁械泻邪 褋褍 懈褕谢邪 褑械褋褌芯屑.'' (''Two men walked down the street.'')
*:Example of plural:  ''袩械褌 褭褍写懈 褋褍 懈褕谢懈 褑械褋褌芯屑.'' (''Five men/people walked down the street.'')

